    RhodsCtrl -->|deploys| ModelRegOp
    RhodsCtrl -->|deploys| TrustyAIOp
    RhodsCtrl -->|deploys| FeastOp
    RhodsCtrl -->|deploys| LlamaOp
    RhodsCtrl -->|deploys| MLflowOp
